All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Control, Container
public class Step3 extends Step
This step asks for confirmation on the client information added through the wizard. If user confirms, the new client is inserted into the database, if user cancels the wizard is ended and user is redirected back to the first step.

Step3 uses a Velocity template (Step3.htm) to render client information.
